<br>
I'd suggest trying to get Thunderous drums of Karana, or drums of the beast.  Also, there's a mace, with brass effect that drops in PoJ trials.  Troubadour's Mace, or so.  And for Strings, check out Lute of the Howler.  As for wind instruments, I still have a few store bought flutes in the bank, in case my epic is sitting on my corpse.  All these are droppable, and can be acquired  in the bazaar for a modest amount of platinum.  The Giant fort in Burning woods, is a decent place to get plat, while still getting xp, at lvl 49.<br>
<br>
